LORE kiess-guard
FLAGS KIESS GUARD
- Wall Command: four watchtowers, gate discipline, patrol rotation; no single
  commander assigned the same post too long — same logic as Kowloon's seasonal
  rotation, different implementation
- Executioner stationed at the Central Prism; violent breach of city law is
  answered immediately and publicly; this is not a deterrent, it is the policy
- Scout debriefing posts in the north ring; returning forest expeditions report
  here; mist-fever casualties processed in central wards
- Forest of Confusion rope-line corridors and bell-post networks through the
  southern verge; do not enter the forest without attaching to a rope-line
- Kiess founding charter explicitly prohibits honoring sealed warrants from
  predecessor authorities; anyone presenting such a warrant is turned away
  regardless of who issued it
- Withered Depths blight progression reports forwarded to Midgaard road warden
  command; this is a standing intelligence-sharing agreement
~
